  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <head>Iḷampūraṇar</head>
      <p xml:lang="en">ed. <persName xml:lang="ta">Namaccivāya Mutaliyār</persName> 1931, <ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZMelJhy.TVA_BOK_0007521/page/168/mode/1up">168</ref>.</p>
      <p>
varalāṟu:
      </p>
      
      <lg xml:id="TolC276-Ilam-cit1">
        <l>‘amma vāḻi tōḻi’</l>
        <trailer>[aiṅkuṟu - <num xml:lang="en">31</num>]</trailer>
      </lg>
      <p>
        eṉṟavaḻi, atu kēḻāy vāḻi tōḻi eṉṟavāṟum. ()
      </p>
    </body>
  </text>
  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <head>Cēṉāvaraiyar</head>
        <p xml:lang="en">ed. <persName xml:lang="ta">Ci. Vai. Tāmōtarampiḷḷai</persName> 1868, <ref target="https://archive.org/details/tolkppiyamcollat00unse/page/n218/mode/1up">215</ref>–<ref target="https://archive.org/details/tolkppiyamcollat00unse/page/n219/mode/1up">216</ref>.</p>
      <p>
i-ḷ. ammaveṉṉumiṭaiccol oruvaṉai oruvaṉ oṉṟu kēḷeṉṟu collutaṟkaṇ varum. e-ṟu.
      </p>
      <p>
u-m. 
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC276-Cena-cit1">
        <l>‘amma vāḻi tōḻi’</l>
      </lg>
      <p>
eṉa varum.
      </p>
      <p>
miyā ika mutalākiya acainilai oruporuḷuṇarttāvāyiṉum muṉṉilaikkaṇallatu vārāmaiyāṉ avviṭamuṇarvikkumāṟupōla, ammaveṉpatūum oruporuḷuṇarttātāyiṉum oṉṟaṉaik kēṭpikkumiṭattallatu vārāmaiyāṉ apporuḷuṇarvikkumeṉpatu viḷakkiya, kēṭpikkumeṉṟār. (28)
      </p>
    </body>
  </text>
  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <head>Nacciṉārkkiṉiyar</head>
      <p xml:lang="en">ed. <persName xml:lang="ta">Irāma. Kōvintacāmipiḷḷai</persName> 1997, <ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZM3kZpy.TVA_BOK_0008472/page/301/mode/1up">301</ref>–<ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZM3kZpy.TVA_BOK_0008472/page/302/mode/1up">302</ref>.</p>
      <p>
‘amma’ veṉṉu miṭaiccolliṉ poruḷ
      </p>
      <lg>
          <l>ammakēṭ pikkum.</l>
      </lg>
      <p>
itu, poruḷ paṭumāṟu kūṟukiṉṟatu.
      </p>
      <p>
(i-ḷ) amma kēṭpikkum ― ammaveṉṉuñ col yāṉ kūṟukiṉṟataṉaik kēḷ eṉṟoruvarkkuk kēṭpikkum poruṇmaiyiṉai yuṇarttaniṟku meṉṟavāṟu.
      </p>
      <p>
colloṭu poruṭ koṟṟumai karutik ‘kēṭpikku’ meṉṟār.
      </p>
      <p>
(u-m)
      </p>
     <lg xml:id="TolC276-Nacc-cit1">
        <l>‘amma vāḻi tōḻi!</l>
      </lg>
      <p>
amma veṉṉu macaiccoṉīṭṭa meṉpuḻiyum poruṭantē niṟkumāṟu kūṟiyavā ṟāṇṭuṇarka (<num xml:lang="en">23</num>)
      </p>
    </body>
  </text>
  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <head>Teyvaccilaiyār</head>
      <p xml:lang="en">1929, <ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZU1k0My.TVA_BOK_0007188/page/n185/mode/1up">178</ref>.</p>
      <p>
ituvum acainilaiccol poruḷ paṭumāṟu uṇarttutal nutaliṟṟu.
      </p>
      <p>
i-ḷ:― amma eṉṉum col acainilai yākalēyaṉṟik kēḷ eṉṉum poruḷum paṭum. e-ṟu.
      </p>
      <p>
u-m:―
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC276-Tey-cit1">
        <l>amma vāḻi tōḻi’</l>
        <trailer>(aiṅ - 31)</trailer>
      </lg>
      <p>
eṉṟavaḻik kēḷ eṉṉum poruḷ kuṟittu niṉṟatu.
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC276-Tey-cit2">
        <l>uṇṭā lammaviv vulakam’</l>
        <trailer>(puṟam - 182.)</trailer>
      </lg>
      <p>
eṉpatu acainilaiyāki vantatu. acainilai eṉpatu eṟṟāṟ peṟutu meṉiṉ, mēl “ammaeṉṉum acaiccol nīṭṭam” (viḷimarapu - 35) eṉpataṉāṟ peṟutum.	[27]
      </p>
    </body>
  </text>
